<div id="c39">
<p>As I said, by the physics of consciousness I mean qualia &#8212; the physical fact that I have conscious subjective experiences. This is so different from every other physical process we&#8217;ve studied that I don&#8217;t see how it could exist without its own physical basis.</p>

<p class="posted">posted by <a rel="nofollow" href="http://www.aaronsw.com/">Aaron Swartz</a>
